title: Light
content:
Light may refer to:

  • Fire
  • Light sources
  • Weight-reducing clothing
  • White, the lightest colour.
  • (light), the item suffix.

NPCs[edit | edit source]

  • Light creature, encountered during the Tears of Guthix quest.

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Demon Slayer items:
    • Silverlight, and its mounted version.
    • Silverlight key (Captain Rovin)
    • Silverlight key (Sir Prysin)
    • Silverlight key (Wizard Traiborn)
  • Light infinity robes:
    • Light infinity hat
    • Light infinity top
    • Light infinity bottoms
  • Light mystic robes:
    • Mystic hat (light)
    • Mystic robe top (light)
    • Mystic robe bottom (light)
    • Mystic boots (light)
    • Mystic gloves (light)
  • Treasure Trail items:
    • Light infinity colour kit
    • Light bow tie
    • Light tuxedo jacket
    • Light trousers
    • Light tuxedo cuffs
    • Light tuxedo shoes
  • Arclight
  • Boots of lightness, an item used in the Temple of Ikov quest.
  • Darklight, an item used in the Shadow of the Storm quest and its mounted version.
  • Light ballista, and its incomplete and unstrung versions.
  • Light box
  • Light frame
  • Light orb, and its empty version.
  • Light tax bag, an item used in the The Fremennik Trials quest.
  • Orb of light, an item used in the Underground Pass quest.
  • Saradomin's light
  • Staff of light
  • Thatch spar light

Other[edit | edit source]

  • Enlightened Journey, a quest.
  • Lighthouse, a location.
  • Lightness, a music track.
  • Light Jungle
  • Temple of Light
